
--- allocconstw arg
allocate arg words on stack

pc++
pc->ml
mr->B
sp->A
[sub]->aluop
aluoe->sp
pc++

--- allocconstb arg
allocate arg words on stack

IRHigh->B
sp->A
[sub]->aluop
aluoe->sp
pc++



=== ARGUMENT FRAME ===

--- addrf arg
get address of [arg]-function argument

[addrf][arg]

sp++
pc++
pc->ml
mr->T
sp->ml
AP/BP=1 TP->mw
pc++


--- addrfb arg
get address of [arg]-function argument

[arg|addrf]

sp++
sp->ml
IRHigh->T
AP/BP=1 TP->mw
pc++


--- iaddrf arg
get address of [arg]-function argument, indir it

[addrf][arg]

sp++
pc++
pc->ml
mr->T
AP/BP=1 TP->ml
mr->A
sp->ml
A->mw
pc++


--- iaddrfb arg
get address of [arg]-function argument, indir it

[arg|addrf]

sp++
IRHigh->T
AP/BP=1 TP->ml
mr->A
sp->ml
A->mw
pc++



